          <text><![CDATA[<p><strong></strong></p> <p> <p><b>Legitimate Use of Medicinal Marihuana Act or LUMMA</b></p> <p>This bill transfers marijuana from schedule I to schedule II of the Controlled Substances Act.</p> <p>It specifies that no provision of the Controlled Substances Act prohibits or restricts activities related to medical marijuana that comply with a state's medical marijuana law.</p> <p>This bill does not affect any federal, state, or local law that regulates or prohibits smoking in public. </p>]]></text>
          <updateDate>2017-01-27T05:00:00Z</updateDate>
        </item>
